public RuleKey.Builder mergeIdempotence(boolean idempotence)
The idempotence of the RuleKey to be built is false if this method is ever called with a false argument.

nonIdempotent

public RuleKey.Builder nonIdempotent()
Non-idempotent RuleKeys can be built by calling nonIdempotent() at any building stage. This method is intended for generation of RuleKeys to be associated with non-cacheable BuildRule results.
